{"tid":1799602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TC Cander 2019 全球百大帥哥榜","createTime":"2019-12-27T05:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T01:28:54.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"04c130287d3f8c7e6faeef87bcadffc9362683a9","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_01p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=2c4ea694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國電影網站TC Candler每年年尾均會公布「全球百大美女排行榜」及「全球百大帥哥排行榜」，今年「全球百大帥哥排行榜」由英國男子組合One Direction（1D）前成員Zayn Malik稱冠，力壓排在第2位的「雷神」澳洲男星基斯漢斯禾夫（Chris Hemsworth）。而曾於前年稱冠榜首的韓團防彈少年團（BTS）成員V，由去年第5位回升至第3位。"},{"pid":"fbb9c438bb0740764050bedf8b45eb41882cc7fc","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"至於憑超級英雄「美國隊長」上位的基斯伊雲斯（Chris Evans）則排第4位。此外，去年高踞第2位的BTS成員Jungkook，今年跌至第17位，隊友Jin排21位，而「臉蛋天才」車銀優則位列第11位，韓團EXO成員世勛亦成功進佔第22位。"},{"pid":"45c70d5998d466e5671cf4b01e48efefb7e9d34e","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"此外，憑《格雷五十道色戒》系列走紅的男星占美杜倫（Jamie Dornan）、土耳其男星Cagatay Ulusoy與澳洲菲律賓混血歌手兼演員James Reid依次排在第5至7位。而英國男星艾迪斯艾巴（Idris Elba）、意大利網上紅人Mariano Di Vaio與巴西男模Marlon Teixeira則分別排在第8至10位。至於上月在內地錄節目《追我吧》期間猝逝的台灣男星高以翔亦進佔第53位。"},{"pid":"4238d5fbe5b8d8229e7fcfd618c93d6f72e69b29","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_02p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=74500fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nZayn Malik稱冠全球百大帥哥榜。"},{"pid":"c69405ea51449edb546e81035c9d8a0f8d7225b3","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_03p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=f5756a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲男星基斯漢斯禾夫（Chris Hemsworth）屈居第2位。"},{"pid":"e315dd734ae689ec8ee7da2148d6923b8943bfca","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":29,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_04p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=c46d5dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防彈少年團（BTS）成員V排第3位，成為榜中排名最高的韓國男星。"},{"pid":"53e0e7d3b3ee85f96b024f5690a8503bd3116f84","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_05p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=454838cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基斯伊雲斯（Chris Evans）排第4位。"},{"pid":"2061daf0fd772019c4b694fbf61f08a8582ee10b","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":13,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_06p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=1d5691e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「臉蛋天才」車銀優位列第11位。"},{"pid":"f9af62ff6f75722dda2dbaa25e54a872a44d9abb","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_07p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=9c73f4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年榮獲第2名的BTS成員Jungkook，今年跌至第17位。"},{"pid":"f47f78543fa1763aab59772dcc87a8a23903d70c","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_08p.jpg?20191227123917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227113114372-1227_00862_001_08p.jpg%3F20191227123917&h=7f66ff0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBTS成員Jin排第21位。"},{"pid":"c47b41d0bf98b2ac54e6f18c6c82eee676100c5d","tid":1799602,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e4cd06127456fd7c171c3cb880c01c4f3f955f","tid":1799602,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https